name: Stir Fry
description:
Your house collapses, sky full of ash. You realize it- far far too late. Your whole village, glory and pride. Was a giant scheme for the world's largest stir fry. Why else would the king request you grow the largest vegetables and not eat them? You are merely a seasoning in the world's largest pan.
